-- ERG Renew, Lukoil to Collaborate in Eastern Europe Renewable Energy Market
-- Dan Liefgreen
-- 2010-07-12T08:08:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/erg-renew-lukoil-to-collaborate-in-eastern-europe-renewable-energy-market.html

          
          
             ERG Renew and Lukoil said they
signed a memorandum of understanding to cooperate in the market
of renewable energy sources, focusing on the wind energy
segment. The companies said in a statement distributed by the
Italian Exchange that they will evaluate opportunities in
Eastern Europe and Russia.  
          
          


  


        